{"tid":913922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【回顧】工黨不支持「派糖」及「全民派錢」","createTime":"2018-11-23T18:58:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T07:56:08.000Z","uid":70063,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c255f89c5a55af3ba3dedc8404152c0b3a5f9970","tid":913922,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T18:58:10.000Z","msg":"議會陣線聯同工黨立法會議員張超雄與財政司司長陳茂波會面，就下月發表的財政預算案表達意見。<br />\n<br />\n人民力量立法會議員陳志全估計今年會有大額財政盈餘，認為政府以往退稅、退差餉的做法是「還富於富」，未能全民受惠，建議直接向市民「派錢」。<br />\n<br />\n工黨立法會議員張超雄表示，工黨不支持「派糖」及「全民派錢」，認為應運用資源，提供足夠服務，提升市民生活質素，期望政府不要愈派糖，愈造成貧富懸殊。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員朱凱迪表示，會面中有討論到香港基建開支是否過高等議題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1374232-20180109.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1374232-20180109.htm&d=oPV7m1N%2BLefFuRADm1MhdIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=78eaee78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1374232-20180109.htm&h=b7cea3ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1374232-20180109.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e84d85cdd79c7cc6600c368cf103ee25fba24dac","tid":913922,"uid":37220,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T19:12:19.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"d46b94924eda68bde3e493a999601f48b0c713c5","tid":913922,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T07:12:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3a1a0fa845951d7e87313b5ac6e3212e80a6d073","tid":913922,"uid":137921,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T07:12:58.000Z","msg":"歡迎張超雄引入南亞狗攪炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a3bce73430532c83919308bcd7b6a5af0678877","tid":913922,"uid":16925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T07:56:08.000Z","msg":"咁用晒個庫房黎幫匡智會好無？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}